{"tid":7911,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟當初邊個話E-kids會考夾埋得5分","createTime":"2016-11-28T05:12:28.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T05:25:07.000Z","uid":7367,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f9b16df7b5d1cd6541575622047f386e084a9f61","tid":7911,"uid":7367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T05:12:28.000Z","msg":"坊間一直盛傳，E-kids三子當年會考加埋不多於5分，呢個謎，Tommy上年喺《蘋果》親自揭盅，方法係返旺角街頭rap歌《Ekids會考五分之謎》（相關新聞： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2gyR8iS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2gyR8iS&d=kZk8JhlaDaUGtptB1ndLt8W%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=e0b4651a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2gyR8iS</a> ）又繼《踩唔死我》之後，再擺自己上枱。<br />\n<br />\n講番呢首《Ekids會考五分之謎》先，佢rap到去尾，好語重深長（甩住beat）咁唱：「好命嘅話你條命仲有七十幾年，所以根本冇人有資格睇你唔起，踩得死你，Yo，講完。」<br />\n<br />\n踩極都未死得，佢先至打破呢個都市傳說，原來E-kids三個加埋，先得一分，而寶貴嘅一分，仲係由Tommy拎嘅，真係點都死唔去。至於另外兩位成員Tim同Alan，Tommy話佢哋連考都冇考過！<br />\n<br />\n點知夾埋都冇五分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1179c3f822d6cc7cabdbc1dccea26fed4cabbcac","tid":7911,"uid":7940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T05:26:03.000Z","msg":"幾十歲人仲叫ekid<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係都叫e佬"},{"pid":"6fd72c27f246eb59809733965f2463b760331209","tid":7911,"uid":9468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T05:31:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"249400b6bcbd3736c22b62335f75313a6d2cb2d0","tid":7911,"uid":24455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T10:18:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"205a46feb1ddd5088b704e1205ca07e1698